### CLIENTS - TESTES
### =========================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@clientId = 2

### Criar um novo cliente
POST {{baseUrl}}/clients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João da Silva",
  "email": "joao.silva@email.com",
  "senha": "senha123",
  "telefone": "11999999999"
}

###

### Criar cliente com email duplicado (erro esperado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/clients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João Duplicaddo",
  "email": "joao.silva@ewmail.com",
  "senha": "senha123",
  "telefone": "11888888888"
}

###

### Listar todos os clientes
GET {{baseUrl}}/clients

###

### Buscar cliente por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/clients/{{clientId}}

###

### Buscar cliente inexistente (erro esperado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/clients/999999

###

### Atualizar cliente (nome e telefone)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/clients/{{clientId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João Silva Atualizado",
  "telefone": "11977777777"
}

###

### Atualizar cliente (email)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/clients/{{clientId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao.atualizado2@email.com"
}

###

### Atualizar cliente (senha)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/clients/{{clientId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senha": "novaSenhaSegura123"
}

###

### Atualizar cliente sem campos (erro esperado)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/clients/{{clientId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
}

###

### Deletar cliente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/clients/{{clientId}}

###

### Buscar cliente deletado (erro esperado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/clients/{{clientId}}
